## ğŸ¨ Customization

Everything in `config.js`:

```javascript
window.PROFILE_CONFIG = {
  musicList: [{ src: 'your-track.mp3', title: 'Song Name' }],
  crawlLines: ["Your poetic line", "Another line"],
  socials: [{ name: 'Platform', url: 'https://...', icon: 'ğŸ”—' }],
  avatarDefault: 'profile.jpeg',
  description: 'Your bio here',
  accent: '#your-color',
  // ... and more
};
```

